  {
    "@id": "https://www.zeffy.com/en-CA/ticketing/femmes-pour-logifem-volume-5-return-of-the-femme",
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Montreal! After a 3 year hiatus, we’re thrilled to invite you all to the 5th edition of the benefit concert Femmes pour Logifem vol V: The Return of the Femmes, at Casa del Popolo. This genre bending musical event will be a night of woman-fronted music bringing together diverse voices. All funds raised will be donated to Logifem. Femmes pour Logifem is a volunteer initiative founded and produced by singer-songwriter, Naghmeh Shafiei. Started in 2019, these live and virtual events have raised over $32,000 to help Logifem financially. Musical performances by:Naghmeh Julie NeffNazaniiLogifem has been a vital part of Montreal since 1988. This organization provides accommodation and support to women and children experiencing homelessness. They offer long term shelter, transitional apartments, and since October 2024, permanent apartments. The vision is to equip and empower women and children to leave the cycle of homelessness and thrive. Event info:Date: March 26, 2026. Doors open at 7 pm, concert starts at 8 pm. Tickets: $20. * Any donation beyond that amount qualifies for a tax receipt.Address: Casa del Popolo, 4873, boul. St-Laurent, Montréal."
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#site_name": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Zeffy"
      }
    ],
